Wednesday, February 19, 1992

MERIT DOCKET

90-2306. State, ex rel. Natgun Corp., v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin County. Appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County, No. 88AP-677. On application for dismissal. Application granted.

Moyer, C.J., Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur. Sweeney, J., not participating.
